*EXP. DATA (T): UFGA2402 Donald Coon lettuce observed time-course data
! Aggregated from /donald coon/ by treatment x variety x DAS; representative cycle dates from UFGA2402.LUX
! TRNO mapping: 1=t1 BG, 2=t1 WG, 3=t2 BG, 4=t2 WG, 5=t3 BG, 6=t3 WG, 7=t4 BG, 8=t4 WG
! Units: FWGP g/plant; CWAD kg/ha from dry biomass at 16 plants/m2; CHTD m; TRRC mL/plant/d; N, C, P, K nutrient columns in %DM
! Sources: biomass_complete_dataset.csv, photos_with_LAI.csv, photos_height.csv, transpiration_corrected.csv,
!          fluorescence_complete.csv, licor-complete-dataset.csv, plant_nutrition_dataset.csv
! Variable units:
! EPAA  = estimated transpiration in DSSAT units (mm/d), converted from TRRC
!         using EPAA = TRRC * 16 / 1000, with 16 plants/m2 from UFGA2402.LUX
! PHAN  = estimated noon gross-photosynthesis units (mg CO2/m2/s), converted
!         from ATOP using PHAN = ATOP * 0.044; unit-converted proxy only
! TRNO = treatment number
! DATE = DSSAT date code (YYDDD)
! DAS  = days after seeding
! FWGP = fresh weight per plant (g/plant)
! CWAD = canopy dry weight (kg/ha), converted from dry biomass at 16 plants/m2
! LAID = leaf area index (m2 leaf/m2 ground)
! CHTD = canopy or plant height (m)
! TRRC = transpiration, evaporation-corrected (mL/plant/day)
! SPAD = SPAD chlorophyll index (unitless)
! LTHK = leaf thickness
! LFTP = leaf temperature (deg C)
! LEFD = linear electron flow density or LEF from PhotosynQ
! PHI2 = PSII quantum yield (unitless)
! ATOP = net CO2 assimilation A (umol CO2/m2/s)
! GSWD = stomatal conductance to water vapor gsw (mol H2O/m2/s)
! CIAD = intercellular CO2 concentration Ci (umol/mol)
! WUED = instantaneous water use efficiency A/E from LI-COR (umol CO2/mmol H2O)
! TLFD = leaf temperature from LI-COR Tleaf (deg C)
! LN%D = leaf nitrogen concentration (% dry matter)
! LC%D = leaf carbon concentration (% dry matter)
! SHKPD = shoot potassium concentration (% dry matter equivalent)
! SHPPD = shoot phosphorus concentration (% dry matter equivalent)
@TRNO  DATE DAS    FWGP   CWAD  LAID  CHTD   TRRC  SPAD  LTHK  LFTP  LEFD  PHI2  ATOP  GSWD   CIAD  WUED  TLFD LN%D  LC%D SHKPD SHPPD   EPAA   PHAN
