! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
! Conversion notes added after observed data table
! 1. TRRC in this file is observed transpiration in mL/plant/day.
! 2. EPAA is DSSAT average plant transpiration in mm/day.
! 3. Conversion used: EPAA = TRRC * 16 / 1000 = TRRC * 0.016.
!    Assumption: plant population = 16 plants/m2 from UFGA2402.LUX planting.
! 4. ATOP in this file is observed net CO2 assimilation in umol CO2/m2/s.
! 5. PHAN is DSSAT noon gross photosynthesis in mg CO2/m2/s.
! 6. Unit-only conversion used: PHAN = ATOP * 0.044.
! 7. PHAN values added here are unit-converted proxies only; they are not
!    biologically identical to DSSAT PHAN because LUT ATOP is net assimilation
!    while DSSAT PHAN represents gross noon photosynthesis.
! -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
